history.content:
Hey guys! I'm Vicky, and I'm a co-president of Web Development at Berkeley. I hope you've all enjoyed these last few summer days before the semester. Recruitment season is upon us, and if you're interested in tech and web development, then you're in luck! We're currently recruiting for the Fall semester and would love to have you on our team.


Web Development at Berkeley is UC Berkeley's hub for all things web development. Whether you've never written a line of code before or you've been coding since forever, this is the club for you! We offer an education branch for those who want to learn full-stack development and a development branch for members to get industry-level development experience working with growing startups.


We hope to see your application and get to know you all!


Interested? Come learn more!
Infosession 1: Wednesday, September 2nd, 7-8PM PST Facebook event

Infosession 2: Monday, September 7th, 8-9PM PST Facebook event

Interest form: Google form


Ready to apply? Fill out our application today!
Application Link


Keep up with us on our socials!
Website: http://www.webatberkeley.org
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/webatberkeley/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/webatberkeley/
Linkedin: https://www.linkedin.com/company/web-dev-at-berkeley/
